The paper discusses the development of autonomous systems capable of explaining their behavior to users, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). The approach proposed in the paper involves modeling the user's level of expertise, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses algorithms for generating explanations, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY).
